      "side": 1,
      "message": "Two reasons I decided not to do this:\n1. It will force all leaf modules to \"link\" to a pretty beefy \u0027server\u0027 package. I expect it may result in dependency cycles in some places.\n2. I want to have very strict control over what modules can do. Some of them will probably end up in a lot of binaries and it is scary to give them unlimited power. At the same time I want to give unlimited power to the direct users of *server.Server, since they use it only in their own binaries not shared with anyone else, so no big deal if their code does something weird (if it must).",
